72 452 :M
-.12(They must only be dereferenced with objects containing the original
member.)A
58 476 :M
<A5>S
72 476 :M
-.12(They may not be cast to a virtual base of the class containing the
original member.)A
23 500 :M
-.11(The second limitation would be subsumed by a rule which disallowed all
pointer to member casts)A
